<HEADLINE> Equatorial Guinea President Praises Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YAOUNDE, August 21 (Xinhua) -- President Obiang Nguema Mbasogo
of the Republic of Equatorial Guinea today highly appraised the
friendly cooperation relations between China and his country.
</P>
<P>
Obiang made the remarks while receiving credentials presented
by Chen Huailong, new Chinese ambassador to the equatorial
country.
</P>
<P>
During the audience, Obiang expressed his country's hope to
expand reciprocal cooperation with China.
</P>
<P>
He said both China and his country are developing countries.
They are facing the same hard tasks of developing economy,
improving people's living standards and upholding state
sovereignty. They would explore the potentiality to promote
further reciprocal cooperation between the two countries. 
