authorities do not know whether the group members visited Panama
as tourists or businessmen.
</P>
<P>
Cedeno said the Church watches closely the activities of the
group and could present a document to the minister.
</P>
<P>
The group members, all Japanese, are now in the Chiriqui
province, northern Panama.
</P>
<P>
The "Moon" group, founded by Korean Sun Myung Moon, tries to
get millions of U.S. dollars through its influence, the Panamanian
Catholic Church said. 
