Relationship of Friendship and Good-Neighborliness Geared to the
21st Century."
</P>
<P>
At the invitation of Prime Minister Datuk Seri Dr. Mahathir, I
have come to this country for an official good-will visit. It
gives me great pleasure today to have the opportunity to meet with
all of you here and deliver a speech at the welcoming meeting
hosted by the famous Institute of Diplomatic and Foreign
Relations. I would also like to take this opportunity to express
