WASHINGTON, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Heavy rains washed out all
four second-round matches scheduled Thursday at the inaugural
303,000-dollar Pro Championships at Boston.
</P>
<P>
Weather permitting, all four matches were to be played Friday,
with the winners perhaps being forced to play two matches in one
day.
</P>
<P>
