Furlan, third seed Felix Mantilla of Spain was scheduled to face
Jeff Tarango of the United States, sixth-seeded Greg Rusedski of
Britain was to take on Filip Dewulf of Belgium and Galo Blanco of
Spain was to meet Hernan Gumy of Argentina. 
