for Education opened here Thursday under the auspices of the
Association for the Development of Education in Africa (ADEA).
</P>
<P>
Ugandan Minister of Education Amanya Mushega said the focus of
the meeting is to prepare for the ADEA's annual meeting to be held
in Ddakar, Senegal in October this year.
</P>
<P>
The Association for the Development of Education in Africa is
an umbrella body for the African education ministers as well as
funding agencies such as the World Bank and UNESCO.
(Uganda-education)
